    h3 Why do we collect your information?

    p We use your information to:

    ul
      li Personalize your experience. (display the most interesting content for you)
      li To improve our service
      li To provide better customer service
      li To send periodic messages (email or SMS or push notification)
      li To provide to third parties who you have expressed explicit interest in connecting with

    p Your information will not be used to: Sell to thrid parties without your explicit consent

