    h3 Third party links

    p Occasionally, at our discretion, we may include or offer third party services on our site. These third-party services have separate and independent privacy policies. We therefore have no responsibility, and can not be held liable for the content and activities of these linked sites. Nonetheless we strive to protect you and ask you to provide feedback in case you encounter negative experiences with the resources we reference.

    h3 California Online Privacy Act compliance

    p We comply with with California Online Privacy Act as well as Childrens Online Privacy Protection Act. We do NOT collect any information from anyone under 13 years of age. Our website, product and services are all directed towards people who are at least 13 years old or older.

